Class GeneratedColumnBehaviour<K extends Cell,V extends NiOutCell>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.behaviours.GeneratedColumnBehaviour<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Behaviour<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GeneratedIntegerBehaviour

    public abstract class GeneratedColumnBehaviour<K extends Cell,V extends NiOutCell>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Behaviour<V>
    an abstract behaviour of a fully-custom aggregated column/measure.
    These entities lack disaggregated cells, instead they populate at the late aggregation phase
